Privacy Policy for Ai Hoshino

Last updated: Jun 19 2025

Thank you for using Ai Hoshino ! This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data.

1. Information We Collect
We do not collect or store any personal information from users.

The bot may temporarily process message content to respond to commands, but no data is saved.

2. How We Use Information
Data is only used to provide bot functionality

We do not share any data with third parties.

3. Data Retention
We do not store user data. Any temporary data is discarded immediately after use.

4. User Rights
Since we do not store data, there is no data to access, modify, or delete.

5. Contact
If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at: nguyenthaiduc0212@gmail.com
